Develop an 8051 ALP to implement the serial communication as per the following 1. 
If the Microcontroller receives a number “1” then generate a square wave for 1 KHz 2. 
If the Microcontroller receives a  number “2” then generate a square wave for 2 KHz 3. 
If the Microcontroller receives a number “3” then generate a square wave for 3 KHz
